15:16.581 --> 15:20.631
<b>...I didn't know that Sanji 
boy was Germa 66's prince!</b>

15:20.931 --> 15:25.801
<b>He didn't mention it at all! How insolent!</b>

15:25.961 --> 15:30.471
<b>Germa has been expelled from the World Government
because of that incident.</b>

15:30.641 --> 15:35.141
<b>Straw boy and Sanji boy...
Just as I expected,</b>

15:35.521 --> 15:39.601
<b>they're becoming the center of 
attention in the Great Pirate Era!</b>

15:35.701 --> 15:39.461
<b>INAZUMA - A TOP OFFICER 
OF THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY</b>

15:39.621 --> 15:43.251
<b>HACK - A SOLDIER OF THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY</b>

15:39.771 --> 15:43.401
<b>The Straw Hats... I'm excited!</b>

15:44.151 --> 15:47.651
<b>Anyway, the top officers are late.</b>

15:45.091 --> 15:50.131
<b>KOALA - FISH-MAN KARATE ASSISTANT INSTRUCTOR
OF THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY</b>

15:47.691 --> 15:50.281
<b>I'm sure they're somewhere near by now...</b>

15:50.611 --> 15:51.961
<b>You're right...</b>

15:52.451 --> 15:56.451
<b>By the way, Sabo,
what have you been doing there?</b>

15:58.621 --> 16:01.671
<b>You kept looking and smiling at 
Luffy-<i>kun</i>'s article too much and</b>

16:01.671 --> 16:03.771
<b>got a cramp in your face, right?</b>

16:03.771 --> 16:05.211
<b>Are you stupid?!</b>

16:05.421 --> 16:07.871
<b>Ring, ring, ring... Clank.</b>

16:08.381 --> 16:09.721
<b><i>This is Lindbergh!</i></b>

16:09.971 --> 16:12.141
<b>What's wrong? Everyone's waiting.</b>

16:12.141 --> 16:15.141
<b><i>Is this Sabo? We're almost there.</i></b>

16:15.351 --> 16:18.811
<b>But there is trouble! 
Mind if we're a bit late?</b>

16:19.181 --> 16:21.771
<b>No. As long as you're okay.</b>

16:22.191 --> 16:23.061
<b>Clank.</b>

16:23.231 --> 16:29.241
<b>Oh, I'm so excited... All the top officers of
the Revolutionary Army will be here!</b>

16:29.401 --> 16:31.861
<b>I get to see Morley-<i>sama</i>!</b>

16:32.031 --> 16:34.121
<b>I love Betty-<i>sama</i> by far the most!</b>

16:34.991 --> 16:39.331
<b>Sabo, we don't wanna waste any time.
Let's assemble now.</b>

16:39.791 --> 16:42.831
<b>We better solidify our plan before they come.</b>

16:43.091 --> 16:45.851
<b>You're up, Chief of Staff.</b>

16:45.851 --> 16:46.751
<b>Yeah...</b>

16:47.301 --> 16:51.151
<b>At the upcoming Reverie, we'll finally...</b>

16:53.131 --> 16:55.471
<b>Declare war....</b>

16:54.281 --> 16:58.661
<b>SABO - CHIEF OF STAFF OF 
THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY</b>

16:56.431 --> 16:58.111
<b>...against the Celestial Dragons.</b>

17:00.351 --> 17:01.931
<b>So they're...</b>

17:02.351 --> 17:03.771
<b>...the captains of...</b>

17:04.561 --> 17:06.021
<b>...the Revolutionary Army!</b>

17:09.071 --> 17:11.781
<b>Why are their four top officers here?!</b>

17:12.111 --> 17:14.661
<b>Gee, boys are so violent!</b>

17:14.661 --> 17:17.471
<b>That's because they like you, dorky Giant.</b>

17:17.471 --> 17:19.291
<b>No way. That's gross!</b>

17:19.611 --> 17:23.211
<b>I checked in with Sabo
so can we do it now, Betty?!</b>

17:23.581 --> 17:25.631
<b>You can't stop me...</b>

17:26.581 --> 17:31.841
<b>No one's answering my question
and what is he mumbling about?!</b>

17:32.011 --> 17:34.561
<b>I won't forgive them!</b>

17:34.561 --> 17:36.551
<b>I don't know why but he got pissed!</b>

17:36.991 --> 17:39.961
<b>What are you gonna do, you pieces of trash?!</b>

17:40.391 --> 17:42.981
<b>Get killed or fight?!</b>

17:44.771 --> 17:47.111
<b>Choose your own destiny!</b>

17:50.071 --> 17:52.071
<b>Being a hero is someone else's problem?!</b>

17:56.281 --> 17:58.491
<b>Maybe you can be a hero!</b>

18:19.101 --> 18:23.891
<b>The townspeople picked up sticks!
Come on, that's hilarious!</b>

18:24.191 --> 18:26.521
<b>Are you gonna fight us?!</b>

18:28.441 --> 18:32.501
<b>I don't know why but I'm inspired
and feel a surge of power!</b>

18:32.501 --> 18:34.611
<b>Let's drive the pirates out of here!</b>

18:35.151 --> 18:37.491
<b>We should fight and protect our country!</b>

18:40.451 --> 18:41.831
<b>That's right!</b>

18:41.831 --> 18:45.001
<b>That's Betty's Pump-Pump Fruit power!</b>

18:45.041 --> 18:49.331
<b>By waving her flag,
she can bring forth people's power from within!</b>

18:49.651 --> 18:52.501
<b>Betty is a flag-bearer of freedom!</b>

18:52.921 --> 18:55.501
<b>Now, advance!</b>

19:00.761 --> 19:03.901
<b>Ha! I guess they don't know 
it hurts when they get shot!</b>

19:03.901 --> 19:05.731
<b>Don't get carried away!</b>

19:08.271 --> 19:10.731
<b>Lind! Karasu! Back them up!</b>

19:10.901 --> 19:12.001
<b>Got it!</b>

19:12.981 --> 19:13.771
<b>Take this!</b>

19:13.971 --> 19:16.101
<b>Cool Shooter!</b>

19:16.821 --> 19:19.701
<b>--It's cold!
--My gun got frozen!</b>

19:19.701 --> 19:22.851
<b>You bastards! Get out of here, pirates!</b>

19:25.041 --> 19:27.761
<b>Don't back down! Cut them up!</b>

19:28.371 --> 19:29.711
<b>Take their weapons away!</b>

19:35.591 --> 19:37.631
<b>The crows took our swords!</b>

19:37.801 --> 19:38.881
<b>Give them back!</b>

19:39.131 --> 19:40.551
<b>Don't stop!</b>

19:40.801 --> 19:44.261
<b>Fight against your fate!</b>

19:45.431 --> 19:46.891
<b>Go away!</b>

19:52.691 --> 19:55.191
<b>What happened to them all of a sudden?</b>

19:55.361 --> 19:56.821
<b>You...!</b>

19:57.691 --> 19:58.991
<b>The milk!</b>

20:01.451 --> 20:04.121
<b>Give it back to me!</b>

20:23.511 --> 20:26.481
<b>--Let's get away!
--We'll make you pay for this!</b>

20:27.891 --> 20:31.801
<b>Peachbeard... His bounty is 52 million...</b>

20:33.061 --> 20:35.311
<b>That's like nothing.</b>

20:35.311 --> 20:40.031
<b>He's just a crappy pirate who could 
only target a country that was weak.</b>

20:41.401 --> 20:44.741
<b>Blackbeard-<i>sama</i> will come after you...</b>

20:45.241 --> 20:48.741
<b>I'm sorry but he doesn't 
care about his subordinates.</b>

20:49.751 --> 20:53.291
<b>Come on, boy! Shut up already!</b>

20:55.381 --> 20:59.051
<b>Hey, you cowardly, weak and foolish people!</b>

21:01.671 --> 21:06.351
<b>If you turn him in to the World Government,
you'll get the bounty.</b>

21:07.181 --> 21:10.261
<b>That'll be 52 million berries.</b>

21:10.561 --> 21:11.641
<b>And that's...</b>

21:11.881 --> 21:13.601
<b>...all yours!</b>

21:16.271 --> 21:18.441
<b>I want you to have this, too.</b>

21:19.901 --> 21:22.441
<b>The Revolutionary Army's contact information.</b>

21:27.741 --> 21:29.831
<b>You did great...</b>

21:29.991 --> 21:30.751
<b>What?</b>

21:32.121 --> 21:33.771
<b>Call us any time...</b>

21:34.371 --> 21:39.921
<b>We'll never turn our back on
the weak who stand up.</b>

21:51.141 --> 21:53.941
<b>B-Belo Betty-<i>sama</i>!</b>

21:59.481 --> 22:03.071
<b>Th-Thank you very much,
everyone of the Revolutionary Army!</b>

22:12.041 --> 22:16.121
<b>Hey, what are we meeting up for this time?</b>

22:16.421 --> 22:18.991
<b>We'll pick a fight with 
the Celestial Dragons.</b>

22:18.991 --> 22:22.711
<b>Oh, that's great! I can't wait!</b>

22:22.711 --> 22:24.341
<b>Oh, and Karasu!</b>

22:25.011 --> 22:26.871
<b>Turn on your loudspeaker switch.</b>

22:30.511 --> 22:31.971
<b>I forgot...</b>

22:34.181 --> 22:36.601
<b><i>It's two days to go until the Reverie.</i></b>

22:37.021 --> 22:41.641
<b><i>All the different intentions across the world
start swirling around...</i></b>

22:43.071 --> 22:44.451
<b>Okay, roger.</b>

22:44.941 --> 22:45.741
<b>Clank.</b>

22:45.901 --> 22:47.701
<b>I got a call, Sabo-<i>kun</i>.</b>

22:48.821 --> 22:50.581
<b>Everyone will be here soon.</b>

22:50.741 --> 22:51.581
<b>Okay...</b>

22:53.291 --> 22:54.791
<b>Let's go...</b>

22:56.751 --> 22:59.671
<b>...to drag down the Celestial Dragons.</b>

23:10.221 --> 23:12.901
<b><i><i>His exploits at Impel Down 
and during the Paramount War,</i></i></b>

23:12.901 --> 23:15.981
<b><i>have earned Monkey D. Luffy 
quite a name in the world!</i></b>

23:16.521 --> 23:18.761
<b><i><i>Inheriting the will of Whitebeard 
and his brother Ace,</i></i></b>

23:18.761 --> 23:21.101
<b><i>Luffy has now become a hero of the age and</i></b>

23:21.101 --> 23:25.321
<b><i><i>the Navy's new Admiral of the Fleet, Sakazuki,
finally shows his teeth!</i></i></b>

23:25.321 --> 23:26.761
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!</b>

23:26.761 --> 23:30.031
<b>"Going into Action!
The Implacable New Admiral of the Fleet - Sakazuki!"</b>

23:30.031 --> 23:32.431
<b>I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!</b>
